stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY TRADITIONAL PARENTING FAILS ADHD KIDS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (ADHD brains process rewards, time, and motivation differently.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (- VISUAL systems \(can't hold info in working memory\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- IMMEDIATE rewards \(delayed gratification is harder\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- SHORTER tasks \(break everything into 5-10 min chunks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- MOVEMENT breaks \(sitting still depletes energy\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- CONNECTION before correction \(shame makes ADHD worse\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
